      "role": "user",
      "content": "i used to be able to see colors in the air... everything was so vivid. now i just look at a canvas and it's like looking into a dark room. i feel like the person who actually made the art is just... gone. like i'm just this empty shell walking around pretending to be a person, but there's nothing left inside.",
